Package org.ejbca.ui.cli.ra

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddEndEntityCommand
    Adds an end entity to the database.
    BaseRaCommand
    Base for RA commands, contains common functions for RA operations
    DeleteEndEntityCommand
    Deletes an end entity from the database.
    FindEndEntityCommand
    Find details of an end entity in the database.
    GetEndEntityCertificateCommand
    Output all certificates for an end entity.
    KeyRecoveryCommand
    Set status to key recovery for an end entity's certificate.
    KeyRecoveryNewestCommand
    Set status to key recovery for an end entity's newest certificate
    ListEndEntitiesCommand
    List end entities with specified status in the database.
    ListNewEndEntitiesCommand
    List end entities with status NEW in the database.
    RenameEndEntityCommand
    CLI command for renaming an end entity.
    RevokeCertificateCommand
    Revokes a certificate in the database.
    RevokeEndEntityCommand
    Revokes an end entity in the database, and also revokes all that end entity's certificates.
    SetCleartextPasswordCommand
    Set the clear text password for an end entity in the database.
    SetEndEntityStatusCommand
    Changes status for an end entity in the database, status is defined in org.cesecore.certificates.endentity.EndEntityConstants
    SetPasswordCommand
    Set the (hashed) password for an end entity in the database.
    SetSubjDirAttrCommand
    Set the Subject Directory Attributes for an end entity.
    SetSubjectDNCommand
    Set the SubjectDN for an end entity.
    UnRevokeEndEntityCommand
    Reactivates end entity's certificates if the revocation reason of user certificates is 'on hold'.
